data.description: Step inside and explore this stunning, move-in-ready home! Recently professionally painted both inside and out. This residence features not one but two kitchen islands, offering abundant prep space and a breakfast bar for comfortable seating. The kitchen is well-appointed with a spacious pantry. With an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, and a generous dining area, this home also boasts a charming built-in reading nook and bookshelves. The main part of the house encompasses three bedrooms and two full baths, while the fourth room is in a private Casita with its own half bath and an expansive walk-in closet. The updated master bath is a highlight, showcasing a fantastic large tiled shower, and the master bedroom includes a convenient walk-in closet. Outside, the low-maintenance spaces include a delightful courtyard and an additional backyard, both featuring beautiful stamped concrete. Enjoy the serenity of a bountiful apple tree and large planter boxes, perfect for cultivating your favorite plants. From the moment you enter through the front door, you'll feel the warmth and charm that make this home inviting. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own--call your preferred agent today for a showing.
